=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}) – {{ill|Hōjō Tokimune|ja|北条時宗|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}, the 8th regent ({{ill|Shikken|ja|執権|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}) of the Kamakura shogunate (died [[1284]]). * {{ill|Tenpō|ja|天保|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 10th year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|ja|グレゴリオ暦|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} [[1839]] {{ill|June 25|ja|6月25日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}) – {{ill|Shimazu Genzō (1st generation)|ja|島津源蔵 (初代)|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}, a businessperson and founder of {{ill|Shimazu Corporation|ja|島津製作所|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} (died [[1894]]). * {{ill|Kaei|ja|嘉永|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 3rd year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|ja|グレゴリオ暦|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} [[1850]] {{ill|June 24|ja|6月24日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}) – {{ill|Baba Tatsuchō|ja|馬場辰猪|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}, a political thinker (died [[1888]]). == Deaths == * {{ill|Genna|ja|元和|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 1st year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|ja|グレゴリオ暦|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} [[1615]] {{ill|June 11|ja|6月11日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}) – {{ill|Sanada Nobushige|ja|真田信繁|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}, also known as Yukimura, a military commander (born [[1567]]). * {{ill|Tenpō|ja|天保|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 13rd year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|ja|グレゴリオ暦|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} [[1842]] {{ill|June 23|ja|6月23日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}) – {{ill|Suzuki Makino|ja|鈴木牧之|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}, a merchant and essayist (born [[1770]]).
