* {{ill|Kaei|ja|嘉永|qq=|12=draft}} 3rd year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=|12=draft}} [[1850]] {{ill|June 24|ja|6月24日|qq=|12=draft}}) – {{ill|Baba Tatsuchō|ja|馬場辰猪|qq=|12=draft}}, a political thinker (died [[1888]]).
