ゴリオ暦|qq=|qq=draft}} [[1868]] {{ill|July 4|ja|7月4日|qq=|qq=draft}}) – During the Boshin War (戊辰戦争), hostilities occurred at Ueno (【Ueno Sensō|上野戦争】): defenders in Ueno, holed up at {{ill|Kan'ei-ji|ja|寛永寺|qq=|qq=draft}}, were overwhelmed by the imperial forces, leading to the new government’s takeover of Edo. == Births == * {{ill|Kenchō|ja|建暦|qq=|qq=draft}} 3rd year ({{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|qq=|qq=draft}} [[1251]] {{ill|June 5|ja|6月5日|qq=|qq=draft}}) – {{ill|Hōjō Tokimune|ja|北条時宗|qq=|qq=draft}}, the 8th regent ({{ill|Shikken|ja|執権|qq=|qq=draft}}) of the Kamakura shogunate (died [[1284]]). * {{ill|Tenpō|ja|天保|qq=|qq=draft}} 10th year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=|qq=draft}} [[1839]] {{ill|June 25|ja|6月25日|qq=|qq=draft}}) – {{ill|Shimazu Genzō (1st generation)|ja|島津源蔵 (初代)|qq=|qq=draft}}, a businessperson and founder of {{ill|Shimazu Corporation|ja|島津製作所|qq=|qq=draft}} (died [[1894]]). * {{ill|Kaei|ja|嘉永|qq=|qq=draft}} 3rd year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=|qq=draft}} [[1850]] {{ill|June 24|ja|6月24日|qq=|qq=draft}}) – {{ill|Baba Tatsuchō|ja|馬場辰猪|qq=|qq=draft}}, a political thinker (died [[1888]]). == Deaths == * {{ill|Genna|ja|元和|qq=|qq=draft}} 1st year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=|qq=draft}} [[1615]] {{ill|June 11|ja|6月11日|qq=|qq=draft}}) – {{ill|Sanada Nobushige|ja|真田信繁|qq=|qq=draft}}, also known as Yukimura, a military commander (born [[1567]]). * {{ill|Tenpō|ja|天保|qq=|qq=draft}} 13rd year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=|qq=draft}} [[1842]] {{ill|June 23|ja|6月23日|qq=|qq=draft}}) – {{ill|Suzuki Makino|ja|鈴木牧之|qq=|qq=draft}}, a merchant and essayist (born [[1770]]).
