0th year ([[:en:Gregorian calendar|Gregorian calendar]] [[:en:1839|1839]] [[:en:June 25|June 25]]) – {{ill|Shimazu Genzō (1st generation)|ja|島津源蔵 (初代)|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Shimazu Genzō (1st generation)|qq=}}, a businessperson and founder of [[:en:Shimadzu|Shimazu Corporation]] (died [[:en:1894|1894]]). * [[:en:Kaei|Kaei]] 3rd year ([[:en:Gregorian calendar|Gregorian calendar]] [[:en:1850|1850]] [[:en:June 24|June 24]]) – [[:en:Baba Tatsui|Baba Tatsuchō]], a political thinker (died [[:en:1888|1888]]). == Deaths == * [[:en:Yuanhe|Genna]] 1st year ([[:en:Gregorian calendar|Gregorian calendar]] [[:en:1615|1615]] [[:en:June 11|June 11]]) – [[:en:Sanada Yukimura|Sanada Nobushige]], also known as Yukimura, a military commander (born [[:en:1567|1567]]). * [[:en:Tenpō|Tenpō]] 13rd year ([[:en:Gregorian calendar|Gregorian calendar]] [[:en:1842|1842]] [[:en:June 23|June 23]]) – {{ill|Suzuki Makino|ja|鈴木牧之|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Suzuki Makino|qq=}}, a merchant and essayist (born [[:en:1770|1770]]).
